    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver for anyone looking for practical transportation. While the engine and transmission are in good working order and the car has been regularly serviced, the exterior shows its age with some noticeable scratches, minor dings, and fading paint in certain areas. The interior is clean but exhibits typical wear on the upholstery and some of the plastic trim. It is a solid, functional car that is ready for the road, though it lacks the polish of a newer or better-maintained model. Expect a dependable vehicle that prioritizes utility over aesthetics.",
