    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Check out this fantastic find! This vehicle is in truly good condition, having been well-maintained and cared for over the years. It offers a smooth, reliable ride and a clean, comfortable interior that makes every trip a pleasure. It\u2019s a solid, dependable car that\u2019s ready for its next adventure with you!",
